vailable in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Wydobywa część łańcucha znaków i zwraca go jako nowy łańcuch znaków.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code><var>str</var>.slice(<var>beginSlice</var>[, <var>endSlice</var>])</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"beginslice\"><code>beginSlice</code>&nbsp;</dt>\n <dd>Oparty na zerze początek indeksu rozpoczynający wyciąganie.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"endslice\"><code>endSlice</code>&nbsp;</dt>\n <dd>Oparty na zerze początek indeksu, który kończy wyciąganie. Jeśli pominięty <code>slice()</code> wydobywa do końca łańcuch znaków.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"opis","title":"Opis","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>slice()</code> wyciąga tekst z jednego łańcucha znaków i zwraca nowy łańcuch znaków. Zmiany w treści jednego łańcucha znaków nie mają wpływu na drugi.</p>\n\n<p><code>slice()</code> wyciąga tekst do <code>endSlice</code>&nbsp;lecz go nie włącza.&nbsp;<code>string.slice(1,4)</code> wyciąga drugi znak aż do czwartego (znaki o indeksach 1, 2 i 3).</p>\n\n<p>Jako ujemny indeks <code>endSlice</code> sygnalizuje przesunięcie z końca łańcucha znaków. <code>str.slice(2,-1)</code> wyciąga trzeci przez ostatni znak w łańcuchu znaków.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ady","title":"Przykłady","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad_zastosowanie_slice_do_stworzenia_nowego_.c5.82a.c5.84cucha_znak.c3.b3w","title":"Przykład: Zastosowanie <code>slice()</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Poniższy przykład używa <code>slice</code> do stworzenia nowego łańcucha znaków.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> str1 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'The morning is upon us.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> str2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> str1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">slice</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">4</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>str2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// OUTPUT: morning is upon u</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Przykład: Zastosowanie slice()"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Podsumowanie","id":"podsumowanie"},{"text":"Składnia","id":"sk.c5.82adnia"},{"text":"Opis","id":"opis"},{"text":"Przykłady","id":"przyk.c5.82ady"}],"summary":"Wydobywa część łańcucha znaków i zwraca go jako nowy łańcuch znaków.","popularity":0.0007,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"String.prototype.slice()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"String.prototype.slice()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"String.prototype.slice()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"String.prototype.slice()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"String.prototype.slice()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"String.prototype.slice()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"String.prototype.slice()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"String.prototype.slice()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"String.prototype.slice()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/string/slice","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/string/slice/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web","title":"Technologie Internetowe dla developerów"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","